    "created_at": "2016-12-07T18:22:45Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-12-07T18:22:45Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This seems like a reasonable request. But it also looks like an API breakage, and I really want to avoid API breakages if at all possible. And there's no indication in the Stream API documentation that `error` and `end` are supposed to be mutually exclusive, so I don't think I can reasonably call the current behavior a bug.\r\n\r\nIf you know of some documentation that indicates that custom streams should behave as you describe, that would help."
  },
